text: Carmen Casteiner, married Cagnotto (born 27 September 1954) is a retired Italian diver. She was born in Bolzano. Casteiner finished nineteenth in the 10 metre platform event of the 1976 Olympic Games. She is the wife of Giorgio Cagnotto and mother of Tania Cagnotto. ==References== Category:Italian female divers Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Bolzano Category:Divers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic divers of Italy
